title: 'Average Product'
body: It's an average quality product which you will feel only after taking the product in your hand. The photo might mislead you into believing that it's a high quality product.  Fact is, this product is a typical example of how an average product competes with superiors products by means of illusionary discounts, photo quality, and putting a lable that it's an Amazon Brand.  Amazon Brand Apparels are pretty average in quality and style.  For clarification, I am not saying they are bad. I am only saying - it's average! And if you were to buy it from a physical store, you wouldn't probably buy it.
